{
  "stem": "2067.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Didn't know what, what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "People got out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The driver got out with his-- a torch-- with a flashlight and came back in again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "People started talking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Then I heard a neighbor of mine say, the English had tried to bomb Le Croisic at night, had bombed the main street.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the bus couldn't continue.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The street was totally destroyed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we turned around, went back to where we had come from, and went a roundabout way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In short, it was about 11:00 at night when we arrived at the bus terminal in Montceau-les-Mines.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] As we heard later form the owner of that pub, he said, what that guy wanted you to do is sit in the back because each bus that comes from Le Croisic, usually two SS guys are standing at the terminal and check the paper of each one that comes out.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's why he wanted you to sit in the back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know what he wanted to do?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He wanted you to be arrested by these SS.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because you had paid him the money?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yes, you did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that's why.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He wanted you to be killed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That was his purpose.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But because of the late hour and the, the destroyed road, the Germans must have thought there is no bus coming anymore.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was no checking of papers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we got off, we could see that guy at the corner.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We rushed after him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He led us through dark streets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then he said, wait here a minute.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have to see that everything is, is, is OK, that's no bad people are there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He went through the back door, left through the front door.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After a few minutes, we noticed he has abandoned us.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
